Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Part1)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孙女亚瑟拉姆被暗杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至没有宣战就与地球开战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该知道杀害亲善大使会造成什么后果才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么还要这样做？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我所不知的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说暗杀者是恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说联合政府对我们没有敌意？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上存在反巴斯势力是可以确定的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管这样 他们还是默许了暗杀行为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以理解成是他们故意松懈护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是联合政府打着恐怖袭击的幌子而自导自演的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下是继承皇族血脉拥有唤醒Aldnoah之力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其血脉自身就代表着巴斯的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人费解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向联合政府提出停战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快去查清事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵旨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战况如何 库鲁迪欧伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京以及周边都市都已在我的占领之下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟拉姆公主的长眠之地新芦原市也已落入我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 托利尔兰男爵现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还在战场上立功吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经…不幸战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战死？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此话当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 太令人遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:05:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不幸地卷入了暴徒在我的领土上所发动的陨石轰击之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 我已经告诉过他轰击这事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不应该会被卷入其中才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托利尔兰男爵作为食客对我鞠躬尽瘁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却以这种方式告别实在惋惜…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为勇敢的战士祈祷冥福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 有人见到托利尔兰男爵最后一面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道亚瑟拉姆公主现在平安无事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样下去…总有一天真的会被暗杀…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧修理！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨磨蹭蹭的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Argyre…那头部…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您平安无事真是太好了 布拉德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫什么没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都名誉扫地了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手很强大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是被橙色的滑头鬼当傻子耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该跟在伯爵身边的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我说了一些僭越的话 所以被他骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僭越的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说希望他允许我一起出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人都会耍小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么想在战场上立功加官进爵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想为公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 这样做就可以自动航行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.22,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(813,655)}autopilot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫妮…妮娜·克莱因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.91,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(715,655)}Nina Klein
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫诘城祐太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫祭阳希咲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们也要参加实战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的 这只是辅修课罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你将敌人的重甲骑兵击退的吗 网文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 马格巴丽吉舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…想出这个作战方案的人是他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战方案？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不觉得这能称得上作战方案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那架练习机的驾驶员吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我叫界冢伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界冢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 界冢雪准尉是我的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好 伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的努力挽救了许多机组人员和平民的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的姐姐也一定会以你为豪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是正规军人的话 我都想为你请功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请功？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指授予勋章
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害啊 可以拿到勋章
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然很厉害了 我从来没有见人拿过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为一直都没有实战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠户教官…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教官？这里可不是学校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了 鞠户上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后勋章也不会是什么稀奇物了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这是战争时期 名誉是唯一可以给予我们的奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了名誉去死也不是什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水深火热之中活着也是很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠户上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以借一步说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在军舰上开业吗？医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不工作没饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏年轻人的梦想可不值得称道啊 上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到你的信任我真是很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你是因为喝醉了才去找刁难那些孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我真的醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉在自身命运的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种子岛报告那件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯下的罪恶会依偎在灵魂上 并永远缠着你不放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况是未被制裁的罪孽 至死都不会得到原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休穆雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:47.29,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humeray
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是你救了他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救了他吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听 听说火星那边提出停战！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}通告愚蠢的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们伟大的巴斯帝国皇帝——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雷伊雷嘉利亚·巴斯·雷巴斯陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}已经向地球联合发布了停战宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们为与你们拥有共同的祖先感到可耻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}希望雷伊雷嘉利亚陛下期待和平的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}能传递给杀害了亚瑟拉姆公主性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}罪恶深重的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我再重复一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们伟大的巴斯帝国皇帝 雷伊雷嘉利亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都无法正常通信了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能收到这种强行入侵线路的广播
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这可以当作是临时休战了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是爷爷想去阻止骑士们的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星的皇帝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷伊雷嘉利亚皇帝向联合政府提出了停战声明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接越过了我们？不和我们轨道骑士打任何招呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须向皇帝进言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往谒见室！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我联络月面基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 并非因为陨石轰击而被干掉的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nilokeras看来是因为战斗而受损后被遗弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我调查一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并继续潜伏在库鲁迪欧城进行调查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单方面开战后又慌慌张张地停战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全想不通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说敌人也并非一条心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与本队取得联络吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 干扰依然非常严重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找这艘船的负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉她我的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 让她将我平安无事的事实传达给巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 这场战争就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了 在传达给皇帝陛下之前那些逆贼就会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此目前这个停战状态对我们来说是最好的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可不是那种老老实实遵守停战协定的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样做只是自寻死路罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 战争拖得越长牺牲者也就越多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想死的话 那么你自便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但请不要将我给卷进去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是停战吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就停战 叫我怎样一雪前耻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…还打算复仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉！你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰载机出击 进行迎击！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 请前往CIC
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下到底在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是他的亲生骨肉被杀死了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织调查团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照陛下的旨意 去调查公主被暗杀的细节
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来…就可以见到皇帝陛下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 让我们继续上次的未竟之战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aldaniti小队 出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号升降梯 上升
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 不要使用HE弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用AP弹进行迎击！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将舰桥当做挡箭牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊？快下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姐才应该回去 你是伤兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员不够用啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我出击也一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡衣放在哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有花斑的那件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是斯雷因·托罗亚特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯雷因？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真是好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要转告给皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…亚瑟拉姆公主其实还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是亲眼见证的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了对地球开战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而向亚瑟拉姆公主下杀手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是轨道骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 暗杀失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟拉姆公主现在还活在地球的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的宿敌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习机？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个难道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈帆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战术套装怎么可能防得住啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.89,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(470,655)}tactical suit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这把刀切不断的铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间将你解决！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.62,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reactive armor
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由炸药所制成的装甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是用于通过爆炸改变敌人的炮弹弹道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过爆炸将敌人刀刃上的等离子驱散吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制塔 请将船体倾斜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见咲！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压舱注水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.06,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,655)}ballast
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船坞式机库 舱门开启！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.78,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,655)}well dock
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背装投掷准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.89,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(526,655)}Backpack
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:48.65,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bailout
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒸汽喷发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把刀的庞大热能使海水集聚蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高压蒸汽产生的冲击破坏了那架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界冢伊奈帆…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无法想像他是个学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 没想到这么有利用价值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见咲 要我告诉你没桃花的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说坦率的性格比较招人喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那不叫坦率 而是口不择言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快去接伊奈帆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你所说的都是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在叫人遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快结束这场战争！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并拯救亚瑟拉姆公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会马上布置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您 皇帝陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公所言不虚 扎赫巴姆伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人都不可信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的间谍无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦有机可乘便图谋颠覆巴斯帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以花言巧语来迷惑失去了最重要的孙女正痛心疾首的陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是胆大包天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给这下贱的种族 赐予正义的铁锤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以巴斯帝国皇帝 雷伊雷嘉利亚·巴斯·雷巴斯之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式宣战！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向地球攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将谋害我血亲的仇人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧殆尽！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯雷因·托罗亚特 打算与我的大义为敌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托罗亚特博士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:10.93,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“谒见殿前”
